a:t.name: description
a:t.value: This library defines functions to convert between FHIR data types and CQL system-defined types, as well as functions to support FHIRPath implementation. For more information, the FHIRHelpers wiki page: https://github.com/cqframework/clinical_quality_language/wiki/FHIRHelpers

message.value: FHIR Quantity value has a comparator and cannot be converted to a System.Quantity value.
